# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# Override the user's global *.sql ignore for migration files.
# Migrations are a deployment artifact — they MUST be committed and pushed.
# Putting the unignore early so global patterns set later (including
# `~/.gitignore_global`'s blanket `*.sql`) don't accidentally re-ignore.
!apps/api/migrations/*.sql
!apps/api/migrations/*.down.sql

# Cloudflare Tunnel credentials
cloudflared/credentials.json

